{"tid":848784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖有真相)   甲午戰爭  「清軍大勝」","createTime":"2018-10-05T07:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T03:16:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b38da0464c532eb9fc9acea7c6587aadc63078e0","tid":848784,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpHnvfjx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpHnvfjx.jpg&h=e56f1a05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖擷取自Mock Mayson Facebook）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國遊客大鬧瑞典事件、關西機場事件，最近中國假新聞頻傳，1名網友在臉書上發文笑指，他去逛英國大英博物館，看到100年前的中國假新聞，才知道原來製造假新聞是中國一直以來的傳統。<br />\n<br />\n網友Mock Mayson昨日在個人臉書上表示，他在大英博物館看到幾張石板印刷的清朝畫報，並列舉了其中3張「朝鮮水戰得勝捷圖」、「威海衛大戰得勝圖」，與「恢復朝鮮得勝捷圖」，這是甲午戰爭結束後，清朝的畫師在「點石齋畫報」上發表了數張「清國軍在甲午戰爭中大勝日本軍的自嗨圖」，當中的幾張。<br />\n<br />\n而當時的中國人還真的相信中國大敗日本，對於真正的戰果完全不了解，如果不是大英博物館收藏了這些清朝畫報，現在的我們還真的很難看到，以前中國人製造假新聞的功力，Mock Mayson嘲諷道，「China從來就沒有什麼自古以來神聖不可分割的東西，只有BullshXt這件事才是China自古不可分割的固有傳統」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇文章在臉書吸引廣大迴響，有近兩千人按讚、超過850次分享，不少網友更贊同地表示「造假是中國人的特質之一！」、「指鹿為馬兩千多年了&hellip;」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkN8Fwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkN8Fwh.jpg&h=19bd43f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPo0AvJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPo0AvJ.jpg&h=8eae0dbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2558686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2558686&d=9poDQFCZBL1sXkIwZgCD0ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=14cd1dec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F2558686&h=ffa87c9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/2558686</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.taronews.tw/files/2018/09/1-5ba343982b97c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.taronews.tw%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F09%2F1-5ba343982b97c.jpg&h=a7f30d5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.taronews.tw/files/2018/09/2-5ba343d6d669b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.taronews.tw%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F09%2F2-5ba343d6d669b.jpg&h=1adec6a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.taronews.tw/files/2018/09/3-5ba34462a31bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.taronews.tw%2Ffiles%2F2018%2F09%2F3-5ba34462a31bc.jpg&h=a7aed7c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：Mock Mayson臉書"},{"pid":"3710bd88120b54e9883ca8eb8ccaa3e05fc0dfe8","tid":848784,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"報喜不報優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9d13518631f904727e0917a8e12b41aeed296a1","tid":848784,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed14e8f9108c0eb018813dfa80d1d01a5f22ed68","tid":848784,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3710bd88120b54e9883ca8eb8ccaa3e05fc0dfe8","tid":848784,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"報喜不報優<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"應該報喜不報劣"},{"pid":"92de0f1eae60eb272afb00f6647eda03505bac30","tid":848784,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3710bd88120b54e9883ca8eb8ccaa3e05fc0dfe8","tid":848784,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"報喜不報優<img src=\